-Come on!
-Look out, dummy, here we come!

180
00:16:01,294 --> 00:16:03,128
We're gonna get you!

181
00:16:04,088 --> 00:16:07,841
Run, Forrest, run! Run, Forrest!

182
00:16:09,552 --> 00:16:11,470
Come back here, you!

183
00:16:25,109 --> 00:16:27,569
Run, Forrest!

184
00:16:27,654 --> 00:16:29,071
Run!

185
00:17:00,269 --> 00:17:03,146
Now, you wouldn't believe it
if I told you,

186
00:17:04,273 --> 00:17:06,775
but I can run like the wind blows.

187
00:17:10,029 --> 00:17:13,115
From that day on,
if I was going somewhere,

188
00:17:13,950 --> 00:17:15,242
I was running!

189
00:17:15,326 --> 00:17:17,703
He's getting away! Stop him!

190
00:17:49,152 --> 00:17:52,154
That boy sure is a running fool.

191
00:17:56,367 --> 00:17:57,743
Now, remember how I told you that

192
00:17:57,827 --> 00:18:00,746
Jenny never seemed
to want to go home?

193
00:18:00,830 --> 00:18:03,915
Well, she lived in a house
that was as old as Alabama.

194
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:06,168
Her mama had gone up to heaven
when she was five,

195
00:18:06,252 --> 00:18:09,588
and her daddy was
some kind of a farmer.

196
00:18:11,424 --> 00:18:12,466
Jenny?

197
00:18:12,550 --> 00:18:14,718
He was a very loving man.

198
00:18:15,178 --> 00:18:19,431
He was always kissing and touching
her and her sisters.

199
00:18:21,184 --> 00:18:25,604
And then this one time,
Jenny wasn't on the bus to go to school.

200
00:18:26,773 --> 00:18:29,649
Jenny, why didn't you come
to school today?

201
00:18:29,734 --> 00:18:31,777
Daddy's taking a nap.

202
00:18:31,861 --> 00:18:33,570
-Jenny!
-Come on!

203
00:18:35,031 --> 00:18:37,574
Jenny, where'd you run to?

204
00:18:38,910 --> 00:18:41,578
You'd better get back here, girl!

205
00:18:43,039 --> 00:18:44,706
Where you at?

206
00:18:48,085 --> 00:18:51,379
Jenny! Jenny! Where you at?

207
00:18:54,383 --> 00:18:55,717
Jenny!

208
00:18:55,802 --> 00:18:58,762
Pray with me, Forrest. Pray with me.

209
00:18:58,888 --> 00:19:00,013
Jenny!

210
00:19:00,097 --> 00:19:03,308
Dear God, make me a bird
so I can fly far,

211
00:19:03,392 --> 00:19:05,143
