212
00:19:05,228 --> 00:19:08,897
Dear God, make me a bird
so I can fly far,

213
00:19:08,981 --> 00:19:10,106
far, far away from here.

214
00:19:10,233 --> 00:19:13,276
Mama always said
that God is mysterious.

215
00:19:13,402 --> 00:19:14,528
Jenny!

