just over on Creekmore Avenue,

221
00:19:29,252 --> 00:19:32,420
which made me happy,
'cause she was so close.

222
00:19:35,007 --> 00:19:40,053
Some nights, Jenny would sneak out
and come on over to my house,

223
00:19:40,137 --> 00:19:43,265
just 'cause she said she was scared.

224
00:19:43,349 --> 00:19:45,809
Scared of what, I don't know,

225
00:19:45,935 --> 00:19:49,145
but I think it was her grandma's dog.

226
00:19:49,272 --> 00:19:51,022
He was a mean dog.

227
00:19:51,774 --> 00:19:54,484
Anyway, Jenny and me was best friends

228
00:19:54,569 --> 00:19:55,861
all the way up through high school.

229
00:19:57,822 --> 00:19:59,865
-Hey, stupid!
-Quit it!

230
00:20:00,992 --> 00:20:03,285
-Run, Forrest, run!
-Hey,

231
00:20:03,995 --> 00:20:05,453
did you hear me, stupid?

232
00:20:05,538 --> 00:20:06,746
-Run, Forrest!
-Come on, get in the truck!

233
00:20:06,831 --> 00:20:08,957
Get in the truck! Let's move it!

234
00:20:09,041 --> 00:20:11,793
Come on, he's getting away! Move it!

235
00:20:11,878 --> 00:20:14,045
Run, Forrest! Run!

236
00:20:14,130 --> 00:20:17,674
-You better be running, stupid!
-Come on, dummy!

237
00:20:19,635 --> 00:20:23,138
-Haul ass, dummy!
-Yeah, you better get running!

238
00:20:26,142 --> 00:20:27,809
Jack rabbit!

239
00:20:36,235 --> 00:20:37,485
Yeah!

240
00:20:38,321 --> 00:20:40,488
Go! Go! Go!

241
00:20:42,199 --> 00:20:43,825
Run, Forrest!

242
00:20:46,829 --> 00:20:50,415
Now, it used to be,
I ran to get where I was going,

243
00:20:52,001 --> 00:20:54,502
I never thought it would
take me anywhere.

244
00:21:23,532 --> 00:21:27,702
